  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_644670dc39220d86b25e26117ef44db2">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>The archive consists of four major types of information:  original manuscript and published materials produced by principles in cold fusion; mass media articles about cold fusion, including newspapers, magazines, books, radio broadcasts, and television broadcasts and consisting of original clippings, off-the-air recordings, computer printouts, digital camera cassettes, and transcripts; taped interviews with researchers, research administrators, public information representatives, and journalists involved in cold fusion; and items of material culture. Also included are 2013 and 2014 History of Cold Fusion Calendar, published by Infinite Energy Magazine.</p>  </scopecontent>
